  <h2>
    <span class="">以下豆列推荐</span>
      &nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;&middot;
      <span class="pl">&nbsp;(
          <a href="https://book.douban.com/subject/1418452/doulists">全部</a>
        ) </span>

  </h2>


    <div id="db-doulist-section" class="indent">
      <ul class="bs">
          <li class=""><a class="" href="https://www.douban.com/doulist/88842/" target="_blank">商务新知译丛</a>
                <span class="pl">(显微无间)</span>
            </li>
          <li class=""><a class="" href="https://www.douban.com/doulist/19319/" target="_blank">艺术</a>
                <span class="pl">(荒 野 地 铁)</span>
            </li>
          <li class=""><a class="" href="https://www.douban.com/doulist/509312/" target="_blank">伊洛书目—哲学思想外国现代哲学第六</a>
